<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="185" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[136,1451,158,365]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">
<bibRefCitation author="Richard, A." box="[136,304,158,184]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" pagination="199 - 219" refId="ref8252" refString="Richard, A. (1841) Tiliaceae. Histoire Physique, Politique et Naturelle de l'Ile de Cuba, Botanique, Plantes Vasculaires 6: 199 - 219." type="journal article" year="1841">Richard (1841)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Richard" authorityYear="1841" box="[423,577,158,184]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platypetala">
<emphasis box="[423,577,158,184]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">L. platypetala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on the 
<emphasis box="[725,973,158,185]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">
<collectorName box="[725,935,158,185]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">Ramon de la Sagra</collectorName>
s.n
</emphasis>
. collection, as reported in the preface. Both Richard and 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:039287B9FFDDFFA1FF43F85FFCD1FE9C:8EE46074FFDCFFA1FED1FF52FE54FF2D" box="[282,415,194,221]" name="De la Sagra" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">De la Sagra</location>
worked in herbarium P, where the collections are kept (
<bibRefCitation author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[1053,1318,194,220]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 758, 1055). In this herbarium we found 
<specimenCount box="[528,708,230,256]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" type="generic">three specimens</specimenCount>
associated with the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Richard" authorityYear="1841" box="[1003,1159,230,256]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platypetala">
<emphasis box="[1003,1159,230,256]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">L. platypetala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Therefore, in accordance with Art. 9.3 of the ICN, we designate herein specimen P 
<date box="[774,886,266,292]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" value="2928-02-14">
<collectingDate box="[774,886,266,292]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" value="2928-02-14">02142928</collectingDate>
</date>
as the 
<typeStatus box="[965,1068,266,292]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Richard" authorityYear="1841" box="[1105,1260,266,292]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platypetala">
<emphasis box="[1105,1260,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">L. platypetala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, by choosing the best-preserved sample and the one that best represents the protologue’s description. The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Richard" authorityYear="1841" box="[1192,1348,302,328]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platypetala">
<emphasis box="[1192,1348,302,328]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">L. platypetala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been considered as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Schumann 1886)" baseAuthorityName="Schumann" baseAuthorityYear="1886" box="[454,790,338,365]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="speciosa">
<emphasis box="[454,580,339,364]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="185">L. speciosa</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Schumann, K." box="[595,782,338,365]" pageId="5" pageNumber="185" pagination="117 - 200" refId="ref8376" refString="Schumann, K. (1886) Tilliaceae. Flora Brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas 12 (3): 117 - 200. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="journal article" year="1886">Schumann 1886</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
